Articles.Content:
SmartParts has two new parts which aren't listed in the file KH\_SSE\_TweakScale.cfg file.  You can fix this by adding the following to that file:

    @PART[km_smart_speed] 
    {
        %MODULE[TweakScale]
        {
            type = free
        }
    }

    @PART[km_prox_sensor] 
    {
        %MODULE[TweakScale]
        {
            type = free
        }
    }
